OL,3,CPrison officer cries as secret
OL,4,Cmessages to inmate exposed
OL,6,FA senior prison officer who had a
OL,7,Frelationship with an inmate cried has
OL,8,Fin court as her secret messages were
OL,9,Fexposed.
OL,11,FAmie Turner, 34, from Bolton, was
OL,12,Fworking as a prison officer at HMP
OL,13,FManchester when she made dozens of
OL,14,Fsecret calls and texts to a prisoner
OL,15,Fusing a smuggled phone.
OL,17,FManchester Crown Court heard phone
OL,18,Frecords showed Turner's number had
OL,19,Fbeen in "sustained contact" with the
OL,20,Fphone between November and December
OL,21,F2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
