OL,3,CPrison officer cries as secret
OL,4,Cmessages to inmate exposed
OL,6,FTurner made 16 and received 28 calls -
OL,7,Fcoming to almost four hours of
OL,8,Fconversation - and she continued to
OL,9,Fcall the inmate beyond his release,
OL,10,Freceiving no reply, prosecutor, Louise
OL,11,FKitchin, said.
OL,13,FShe was arrested while on duty in July
OL,14,F2024, and initially denied any
OL,15,Fknowledge of contact with prisoners,
OL,16,Fbut later pleaded guilty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
