OL,6,FRecorder Jennifer Cleeve told Turner:
OL,7,F"You conducted an inappropriate
OL,8,Frelationship."
OL,10,FShe said the defendant's explanation
OL,11,Ffor her behaviour was 'woeful', adding
OL,12,Fthat she had committed a "serious
OL,13,Fabuse of trust" that undermined
OL,14,Fdiscipline within the prison system.
OL,16,FShe said: "Your culpability is high.
OL,17,FYou were fully aware that mobile
OL,18,Fphones are not permitted in prison.
OL,19,FYou know your behaviour was
OL,20,Fproblematic."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
