OL,3,CPrison officer cries as secret
OL,4,Cmessages to inmate exposed
OL,6,FThe court heard Turner had previously
OL,7,Freceived a final written warning in
OL,8,F2020 over misconduct connected to her
OL,9,Femployment, which the defence said was
OL,10,Fa matter 'entirely dissimilar' to the
OL,11,Flater offences.
OL,13,F"Your behaviour leads to a corrupt
OL,14,Fsystem," the judge added. "This is the
OL,15,Fcorruption that the prohibition on
OL,16,Fphones in prison intends to prevent.
OL,18,F"Your role as a prison officer is
OL,19,Fprecisely to ensure that those on the
OL,20,Foutside are kept safe from inmates."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
