OL,3,CPrison officer cries as secret
OL,4,Cmessages to inmate exposed
OL,6,FTurner cried as she was sentenced to a
OL,7,Fyear and three months, after pleading
OL,8,Fguilty to misconduct in a public
OL,9,Foffice and encouraging and assisting
OL,10,Fthe use of a mobile phone in prison.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Brian Morley said:
OL,13,F"This case highlights the serious
OL,14,Fconsequences of corruption within the
OL,15,Fprison system.
OL,17,F"We will continue to work tirelessly
OL,18,Fwith partner agencies and police
OL,19,Fforces across the region to root out
OL,20,Fsuch behaviour and ensure the
OL,21,Fintegrity of our prisons.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
