OL,6,F"We want to reassure the honest,
OL,7,Fdedicated, and hardworking prison
OL,8,Fstaff that through partnership working
OL,9,Fwith our prisons across the region,
OL,10,Fand the HMPPS Counter Corruption Unit,
OL,11,Fwe will continue to take action
OL,12,Fagainst people who choose to engage in
OL,13,Fcorrupt activity."
